column1: # A manually compiled list of all calibration images from the Energy Farm rhizotron experiment
# First 9 columns: image name and calibration as determined by CKB by tracing each image in Preview.app.
# Columns 10-14: calibration file name and calibration as recorded by tracing techs and used in the now-current version of the WinRhizo data files.
# The next thing I did after compiling this was to re-export the days that seemed incorrectly calibrated
column2: so future readers should treat the values in columns 10-14 as historical.
